絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"3c6e6494f43a79461d45d39c050818920605a8a7","tid":1777181,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:54:18.000Z","msg":"del post啦屌！"},{"pid":"3006672f00be0d0a577ed0d572ba346ef97c2ffd","tid":1777181,"uid":149771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:55:09.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"154690fbada9c5dc22c660d91ed26f80bb4659a2","tid":1777181,"uid":125911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f02571c32a73fd77e84b571ca042f5c40f9b6de3","tid":1777181,"uid":49853,"like":130,"dislike":4,"score":126,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似係西貢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:55:58.000Z","msg":"靜靜地贏唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0243853d3828dadc7cfd53f75e1a2213859fab06","tid":1777181,"uid":321913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T09:02:09.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"58d55b4330ce979c1c2a2af0167d714b2e40d5a4","tid":1777181,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T09:21:37.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"601a6fc85103cc54e38079944844e779990b3fd0","tid":1777181,"uid":273576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T09:22:36.000Z","msg":"樓主。你係咪cls架"},{"pid":"ab221a9893b71ccbbe91f9356e1decf5ec926db9","tid":1777181,"uid":11328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T09:24:52.000Z","msg":"靜靜地贏唔得嘅？"},{"pid":"7dfb27bf